    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsfullscreenmodeapplicationpresentationoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is contained in the options dictionary, the presentation options that were in effect when this method is invoked are not altered, and no displays are captured."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you do not wish to capture the screen when going to full screen mode, you can add "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsfullscreenmodeapplicationpresentationoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to the options dictionary with the value returned by the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsapplication/1428664-presentationoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsfullscreenmodeapplicationpresentationoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " options is specified, exiting full screen mode using "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483256-exitfullscreenmodewithoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " will restore the previously active "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsapplication/1428664-presentationoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Special Considerations",
          "anchor": "1680800"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In OS X v 10.5, invoking this method when the view was not in a window would cause an exception. In macOS 10.6 and later, you can now send this message to a view not in a window. For applications that must also run in OS X v 10.5, a simple workaround is to place the view in an offscreen dummy window."
            }
          ]
        }
